+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0-or-later
+/*
+ * Cedrus VPU driver
+ *
+ * Copyright (C) 2013 Jens Kuske <jenskuske@gmail.com>
+ * Copyright (C) 2018 Paul Kocialkowski <paul.kocialkowski@bootlin.com>
